#circuitbreakersg day 41

Cheat day with some air-fried finger food:

Chicken dippers from @cpfoodssg 
Fried prawn roll from @freshfood_mrjoy 
Farmland Onion rings and Crinkle cut fries
Muar Otah
Pan-fried Tau kwa
Stir-fried Pea sprout & Tau kwa

The green sauce is actually guacamole dip from @californiacreamery 
#jxeatshome #stayhome
Wahhhh all my favourite😍😍😍😍what a delicious spread💕💕💕
@andrew_yc 😅😅😅 u can get it from supermarkets!
Let me take some for dinner
@tamjiak_veggiez yes! air fryer is life saviour 😂
These are making me drool right now ❤️
